    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>ほんじつはたのもう<a href="https://www.riyuzaixianfanyi.com/w/%E9%A0%BC%E3%82%82%E3%81%86">頼もう</a></p><blockquote><blockquote><p>今日就有劳了！</p></blockquote></blockquote><span id="more"></span><h1 id="我是大標題"><a href="#我是大標題" class="headerlink" title="我是大標題"></a>我是大標題</h1><p>随便写点什么<br><em>Ich bin italic</em><br><strong>Ich bin bald</strong><br><em><strong>Ich bin italic und bald</strong></em><br><del>Ich bin durchgestrichen</del><br>x^2</p><h2 id="我是二當家"><a href="#我是二當家" class="headerlink" title="我是二當家"></a>我是二當家</h2><p>oops 是二標題  </p><p><a href="http://www.google.com/">我是超链接1</a><br>我是超鏈接2<a href="https://tophub.today/">https://tophub.today/</a><br>參考文獻：[我是超鏈接3][1]<br>[1]:<a href="http://www.moc.goc.cn/">http://www.moc.goc.cn/</a></p><ul><li>選角色</li></ul><ul><li>做任務</li></ul><ul><li>打怪升級</li></ul><center><img src="/images/鸟巢剪影.jpg" width="50%" height="50%"></center><!--<img src="/2021/05/15/test/%E9%B8%9F%E5%B7%A2%E5%89%AA%E5%BD%B1.jpg" class="" title="鸟巢">--><p><img src="/images/%E9%B8%9F%E5%B7%A2%E5%89%AA%E5%BD%B1.jpg" alt="鸟巢"></p><figure class="highlight django"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs django"><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/images/鸟巢剪影.jpg&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">width</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;50%&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">height</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;50%&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!--</span></span><span class="hljs-template-tag">&#123;% <span class="hljs-name">asset_img</span> 鸟巢剪影.jpg 鸟巢 %&#125;</span><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-comment">--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="xml">![鸟巢](/images/鸟巢剪影.jpg)</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>]]></content>
    
    
